Package daveayan.gherkinsalad.components

Interface Summary
BrowserElement Interface to describe any element on a browser.
CanBeDisabled Interface that indicates that a browser element can be disabled.
CanBeEnabled Interface that indicates that a browser element can be enabled.
Clickable Interface that indicates that a browser element can be clicked.
DatePicker Interface that describes a date picker.
Selectable Interface that indicates that a browser element has multiple options from which one can be selected.
TextEnterable Interface that indicates that text can be entered in the BrowserElement.
 

Class Summary
NullBrowserElement Implementing the Null Object Pattern this object is returned back if an element cannot be found on the browser.
